outputs.output_descr: In light of the global consultation process, Albania will organize its consultation process as (1) addressing inequalities in multiple areas of social development (led by UNICEF and UNWOMEN; (2) inclusive economic development, proxied by productive, decent work in the context of  youth employment (led by ILO and UNDP) and (3) environmental sustainability with focus on biodiversity and climate change / resilience as aspects of sustainable development (led in country by UNDP).

project_descr: RCO - The Future we Want - Post MDGs
project_title: RCO - The Future we Want - Post MDGs
